In order to further improve flood prevention and typhoon prevention work, China Eastern Airlines Technology Co., Ltd. has established an emergency rescue reserve team to carry out flood and disaster prevention knowledge training. It also formulates flight plans based on daily weather and typhoon warning conditions to prepare for aircraft parking in coastal areas. Preparatory work and related emergency plans before operation recovery.
