Our reporter Shang Rui reported: Recently, the Atmospheric Environment and Bioenergy Team of Tianjin University has made significant progress in &quot;membrane separation method to capture carbon dioxide&quot; and successfully developed a new mixed matrix membrane preparation technology, which greatly improved the carbon dioxide capture performance of membrane materials.
