How to make the membrane material &quot;breathe deeply&quot; and improve the gas separation efficiency is the bottleneck and difficulty in using the membrane separation method to capture carbon dioxide.
The scientific research team of Tianjin University developed innovative ideas and explored the impact of different solvents on membrane gas separation performance through repeated experiments.
